\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
One Voice Rule
\series default
:
 The IT Director,
 or the designated Incident Commander,
 shall serve as the sole authoritative source for strategic and public-facing messaging during a cybersecurity incident or infrastructure crisis.
 No Information Operations Personnel shall speculate in writing or verbally on incident cause,
 attribution,
 or scope until authorized by the IT Director or the Incident Commander.
\end_layout

